
We are giving an overview on the oncological patients of the University Children's Hospital at Rostock, exclusively systemic malignancies and brain tumors, for the period January, the 1st 1971 till December, the 31st 1985. The analysis was done in 99 children, 54 girls and 45 boys, aged 0 till 15 years, in whom were diagnosed 30 benign, 1 semimalignant and 68 malignant tumors. We are demonstrating the results of treatment, the age and sex distribution, and the course of the disease, especially in 3 casuistics.

